@page "/multisport"
@layout MainLayout

<PageTitle>Multi-sport — My Mountain Adventures</PageTitle>

@*
    Subview dedicated to aggregate "multi-sport" collections produced by
    the merge feature. Each card pulls together several Strava workouts
    (Running + WeightTraining + Ride etc.) under one title with summed
    totals; the per-activity Strava links live on the detail page
    (Item.razor → TrainingPanel → "Source activities" table).

    Re-uses the standard CategoryGallery so filtering, the thumbnail
    rail and the upload affordance behave identically to the regular
    sport pages — the only difference is the data source (every
    collection whose Category == VideoCategories.MultiSport).
*@
<CategoryGallery
    Category="@VideoCategories.MultiSport"
    BackgroundImage="/images/mountains-bg.jpg"
    EmptyMessage="No multi-sport collections yet. Merge two or more workouts from any category to create one." />
